FRONTLINE ROADS v0.32.2 COLLAPSE AND RECOVERY BALANCE AUDIT

Release: 0.32.2-collapse-recovery-balance
Scope: defensive-collapse pacing, repeated city-defeat loss, ruin repair affordability and restart time

Selected balance:
- Defense destruction pauses new enemy-base launches for 150 seconds.
- City defeat regroup: 210 seconds at civilization Lv.0; 150 seconds at Lv.1+.
- City HP after defeat: 60% at Lv.0; 50% at Lv.1+.
- City recovery: starts after 75 seconds at 0.12 HP/second.
- City defeat requested loss: Lv.0 wood 10 / stone 6; Lv.1+ wood 22 / stone 14.
- Protected repair reserve: Lv.0 wood 50 / stone 40; Lv.1+ wood 80 / stone 60.
- Tower and support-facility full-ruin repair basis: 55% of rebuild cost.
- Dedicated barrier repair tables remain unchanged.
- Repaired towers restart after 20 seconds through the existing disabled timer.

